    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that's ready for its next chapter! It's in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear from its years of service, but it still has plenty of life left to give. With a little bit of maintenance and some light care, this vehicle will make a fantastic, budget-friendly companion for all your travels!",
