    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition and is perfect for someone looking for a reliable vehicle without the premium price tag of a showroom-quality model. The exterior shows noticeable signs of age, including several scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, but the cabin remains functional and comfortable. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak shape. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
