      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are privileged to offer this superlative automotive specimen, presented in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated for the most discerning enthusiast, exhibiting a level of preservation that is truly beyond reproach. From its flawless exterior contours to its pristine, untouched interior cabin, every detail confirms a history of meticulous stewardship. This is a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle that remains in peerless mechanical and aesthetic state, offering an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery.",
